short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A chrome extension to hide the Google AI responses to searches

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AI is great sometime, but sometimes it can be really annoying, especially when you are looking something up and Google gives you an AI response with potentially incorrect information! This tool removes the AI responses, so you can be more confident in the results that you see.
